
& melee_specialist
 
 >> Help: Melee Specialist (Advantage)
 -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
 When performing melee attacks, you receive a -1 on attacker's movement mods
 (lowest 0).
 Increase your melee damage by +1.
 
 Result: You are better at performing melee attacks since this advantage
 lessens/negates your enemy's movement mods. When you hit with your melee
 attack, you hit for more damage.
 
 For a detailed look at this advantage, see our online documentation:
 docs.btmux.com/index.php/Skills%2C_Stats%2C_Attributes%2C_and_Advantages
 
